    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in solid shape and has been super well-maintained over the years\u2014perfect for anyone who needs a reliable, comfy car for daily commutes or weekend road trips. It runs like a dream and is ready for its next big adventure! I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
