    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS system that has been recently overhauled for precision timing. The power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a mechanical limited-slip differential. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced to maintain structural rigidity under high torque loads. The suspension retains its factory-spec MacPherson strut and multi-link geometry, providing the communicative feedback this chassis is known for. While showing minor aesthetic wear consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains mechanically sound with consistent compression across all cylinders. A true analog performer for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Clean title. Maintenance records available. Runs well. No major defects.",
      "price": 34500.0,
