    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a high-revving valvetrain. Mated to a crisp 6-speed manual, the drivetrain benefits from a recent Vanos overhaul and a reinforced rear subframe to address common chassis fatigue points. Suspension geometry remains tight with upgraded polyurethane bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the factory limited-slip differential translates every bit of torque to the tarmac. A driver-focused example with mechanical integrity at its core.",
